{
  "texts": [
    "In addition to these important reference points, we also provide results from off-the-shelf, i.e.",
    "not fine-tuned, models (no asterisks) alongside fine-tuned models (indicated with asterisks).",
    "The fine-tuned generative models performed well compared to standard benchmarks.",
    "They exceeded performance of BERT (base), fine-tuned GPT-3.5, and the combination of LSTM, CNN, and attention mechanisms.",
    "Although none of the models achieve the current SOTA performance (a distinction held by NPCR), each individual model surpasses many previous benchmarks."
  ]
}